tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE bartender_schedule (
  bartender_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  shift_date DATE,
  shift_time TIME,
  availability BOOLEAN
)

CREATE TABLE bartender_schedule (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    bartender_id INT,
    shift_date DATE,
    shift_start_time TIME,
    shift_end_time TIME
);

CREATE TABLE bartender_availability (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    bartender_id INT,
    available_date DATE,
    available_start_time TIME,
    available_end_time TIME
);

CREATE TABLE BartenderShifts (
  bartender_id INT,
  shift_id INT,
  FOREIGN KEY (bartender_id) REFERENCES Bartenders(bartender_id),
  FOREIGN KEY (shift_id) REFERENCES Shifts(shift_id),
  PRIMARY KEY (bartender_id, shift_id)
);

CREATE TABLE Availability (
  bartender_id INT,
  date DATE,
  is_available BOOL,
  FOREIGN KEY (bartender_id) REFERENCES Bartenders(bartender_id),
  PRIMARY KEY (bartender_id, date)
);
